channel.title: Missing worlds?
channel.description: Take a look at this picture [img]http://img159.imageshack.us/img159/9681/screenshot1ag6.jpg[/img] If you look closely, you see that world 60 and 73 are missing, no idea why. They're both members worlds, Jagex should pay us back because they have taken 2 members worlds away! :mad:

item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Worlds go from time to time, I remember, about 2 weeks after Aryan’s release, they removed the default world(76) for an hour one night. But don’t forget, German and RSC take up 4 servers. I’m 100% sure, the servers are named from the date purchased, and just moved around(ie, world 24(UK) to USA) on the average amount of players on each. It would make more sense to move a world located in the USA to the Netherlands if it has the most logins from the Netherlands.
